# Dependencies
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store

# Python
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/env/
**/.venv/

# Git / editor
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store

# Environment files (never send secrets into image)
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Build outputs (rebuilt inside container)
**/dist/
**/build/
**/staticfiles/

# Docker files themselves
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*
**/compose.y*ml
